2007-11-20 19:46 +0100  Rocco Rutte  <pdmef@gmx.net>  (96f931ae0b22)

	* doc/manual.xml.head, init.h: Document that save-hook/fcc-hook/fcc-
	save-hook use $index_format expandos. Closes #2135.

